Job Description
The primary responsibility will be to take leadership role in providing Applications and Technical support to Angola country to Customers and LBP by managing all Fisher quotations to LBPs and Customers in the Region.
Process RFQs, prepare and manage Fisher quotations on time to Angolan Customers
Provide Applications Engineering, Technical and Pricing Support to our LBP in Angola
Collaborate with and support Fisher sales representatives in the country
Work with consultants, customers and endusers to get Fisher products and solutions pre-specified / pre-selected
Work with customers and endusers to update and modify their engineering standards and specifications to gain preference for Fisher
Co-ordinate with Project Management / Order Entry / Customer Order Fulfilment (COF) team to provide clean orders to Factories. and over of orders with supporting documents and attend kick off meetings if required
Ensure Emerson Ethics and trade compliance procedures are strictly followed with all business transactions
Keep up to date with developments in products, industries and market trends
Fulfill any other reasonable duties as required
Job Requirements
Graduate Engineer in discipline like Mechanical / Instrumentation Engg.Â etc.
2-5 years experience in instrumentation industry.
Inside Sales / Application engineering experience required.